					.content
						h1 The 6 Steps of CBM with the PI System
						p Using the PI System for CBM provides multiple advantages. For instance it:
						ul
							li alters the process from a static or periodic assessment to an online, dynamic, real-time assessment of asset health 
							li provides a comprehensive data environment that can be used to conduct a more complete analysis of current conditions
							li transforms real-time data into useful information and creates event frames to supplement this highly detailed data analysis
							li provides the ability to efficiently perform root cause analysis, in case of a failure
		.container-fluid.widthfix#s4
